Commande arduino :

All the command must hav 4 byte so complete with 0 (exemple stop : S000)
	
	- Turn	4 bytes [t][Sign][valueHighByte][valueLowByte] Turn the roomba in the sign direction by the value (from -500 to 500 mmps)
	- Drive 4 bytes [d][Sign][durationHighByte][durationLowByte] Move the roomba for the duration given (in millisecond)
	- Move	4 bytes [m][Sign][valueHighByte][valueLowByte] Move the roomba in the sign direction by the value
	- Stop	1 byte  [s] Stop the roomba
	- Angle	1 byte  [a] Ask the angle of the roomba
